name: NSFileProviderEnumerationObserver
desc: An observer that receives batches of items during enumeration.

items.name: func didEnumerate([NSFileProviderItemProtocol])
items.desc: Provides a batch of enumerated items.

items.name: func finishEnumerating(upTo: NSFileProviderPage?)
items.desc: Tells the observer that all of the items have been enumerated up to the specified page.

items.name: func finishEnumeratingWithError(Error)
items.desc: Tells the observer that an error occurred during item enumeration.

items.name: var suggestedPageSize: Int
items.desc: The page size that the system recommends.
